text: Beyonce Shares Cute Snapchat Pic With Blue Ivy After Coachella Cancellation by Latifah Muhammad 6:55   Playing Beyonce Shares Cute Snapchat Pic With Blue Ivy After Coachella Cancellation Does Beyonce have a secret Snapchat account? The pregnant 35-year-old singer shared a sweet photo of her and daughter Blue Ivy using the infamous Snapchat Bambi filter on Thursday, hours after she postponed her headlining turn at this year's Coachella Valley Music Festival.
